"children":156,"page":42},"高级用法","i-lucide-code-xml","/docs/advanced","docs/7.advanced",[157,161,165,169,173,177,181,185],{"title":158,"path":159,"stem":160},"全文搜索","/docs/advanced/fulltext-search","docs/7.advanced/1.fulltext-search",{"title":162,"path":163,"stem":164},"原始内容","/docs/advanced/raw-content","docs/7.advanced/2.raw-content",{"title":166,"path":167,"stem":168},"SQL 存储","/docs/advanced/database","docs/7.advanced/3.database",{"title":170,"path":171,"stem":172},"调试工具","/docs/advanced/tools","docs/7.advanced/4.tools",{"title":174,"path":175,"stem":176},"钩子","/docs/advanced/hooks","docs/7.advanced/5.hooks",{"title":178,"path":179,"stem":180},"自定义来源","/docs/advanced/custom-source","docs/7.advanced/6.custom-source",{"title":182,"path":183,"stem":184},"LLM 集成","/docs/advanced/llms","docs/7.advanced/7.llms",{"title":186,"path":187,"stem":188},"转换器","/docs/advanced/transformers","docs/7.advanced/8.transformers",{"title":190,"icon":191,"path":192,"stem":193,"children":194,"page":42},"Nuxt Studio","i-lucide-monitor","/docs/studio","docs/8.studio",[195,199,203,207,211,215],{"title":196,"path":197,"stem":198},"设置","/docs/studio/setup","docs/8.studio/1.setup",{"title":200,"path":201,"stem":202},"同步","/docs/studio/github","docs/8.studio/2.github",{"title":204,"path":205,"stem":206},"内容编辑器","/docs/studio/content","docs/8.studio/3.content",{"title":208,"path":209,"stem":210},"媒体库","/docs/studio/medias","docs/8.studio/4.medias",{"title":212,"path":213,"stem":214},"应用配置","/docs/studio/config","docs/8.studio/5.config",{"title":216,"path":217,"stem":218},"本地调试","/docs/studio/debug","docs/8.studio/6.debug",{"id":220,"title":221,"body":222,"description":402,"extension":403,"links":404,"meta":405,"navigation":406,"path":201,"seo":407,"stem":202,"__hash__":408},"docs/docs/8.studio/2.github.md","Studio 与 GitHub 之间的实时同步",{"type":223,"value":224,"toc":392},"minimark",[225,232,236,253,255,264,273,277,280,324,339,355,358,366,373,376,379],[226,227,228],"tip",{},[229,230,231],"p",{},"本节解释了 Studio 与 GitHub 之间的同步行为。此过程直接由平台处理，无需任何外部操作。本页面的目的是提供纯粹的信息。",[233,234,235],"h2",{"id":235},"概述",[229,237,238,239,246,247,252],{},"Nuxt Studio 集成了 ",[240,241,245],"a",{"href":242,"rel":243},"https://github.com",[244],"nofollow","GitHub"," API，实现 Studio 与您的 GitHub 仓库之间的顺畅同步。这一顶级集成是通过利用 ",[240,248,251],{"href":249,"rel":250},"https://docs.github.com/en/developers/apps/getting-started-with-apps/about-apps#about-github-apps",[244],"GitHub 应用"," 实现的。",[233,254,12],{"id":12},[229,256,257,258,263],{},"在创建 Studio 项目时，您需要在您的个人账户或您管理的组织中安装 ",[240,259,262],{"href":260,"rel":261},"https://github.com/apps/nuxt-studio",[244],"Nuxt Studio GitHub 应用","。安装 GitHub 应用需要组织所有权或仓库中的管理员权限。如果您没有必要的权限，仓库所有者需要批准该请求。",[229,265,266,267,272],{},"您可以通过点击应用内的任意位置的 ",[240,268,271],{"href":269,"rel":270},"https://github.com/apps/nuxt-studio/installations/new",[244],"使用 GitHub 安装"," 访问安装页面。",[274,275,276],"h3",{"id":276},"权限",[229,278,279],{},"安装我们的 GitHub 应用时，系统会提示您授予某些权限：",[281,282,283,303],"ul",{},[284,285,286,287,291,292,291,295,298,299,302],"li",{},"对 ",[288,289,290],"code",{},"actions","、",[288,293,294],{},"metadata",[288,296,297],{},"members"," 和 ",[288,300,301],{},"plan"," 的读取权限",[284,304,286,305,291,308,291,311,291,314,291,317,298,320,323],{},[288,306,307],{},"secrets",[288,309,310],{},"administration",[288,312,313],{},"contents",[288,315,316],{},"pages",[288,318,319],{},"pull requests",[288,321,322],{},"workflows"," 的读写权限",[229,325,326,327,329,330,332,333,335,336,338],{},"我们需要对 ",[288,328,290],{}," 的读取权限，以便在拉取请求或仓库默认分支的工作流运行失败时发送通知。",[288,331,294],{}," 是必需的，用于获取仓库数据，",[288,334,297],{}," 用于导入您的组织成员和仓库协作者，",[288,337,301],{}," 用于根据您的 GitHub 账户计划推荐功能。",[229,340,341,342,291,344,291,346,291,348,291,350,298,352,354],{},"Nuxt Studio 代表您创建仓库、分支、拉取请求，并执行提交和合并。我们还提供一键部署到 GitHub Pages，支持工作流和环境变量密钥的即时预览和管理。为实现此目的，我们需要对 ",[288,343,310],{},[288,345,313],{},[288,347,316],{},[288,349,319],{},[288,351,322],{},[288,353,307],{}," 的读写权限。",[274,356,357],{"id":357},"仓库安装",[229,359,360,361,365],{},"安装我们的 GitHub 应用时，系统会提示您选择所有仓库或其中的子集。此选择可随时通过访问 ",[240,362,364],{"href":269,"rel":363},[244],"GitHub 应用设置"," 进行更改。",[229,367,368,369,372],{},"点击 ",[288,370,371],{},"Install"," 后，Nuxt Studio 会安装您所选的每个仓库，使您能够执行上述所有操作。",[233,374,375],{"id":375},"卸载",[229,377,378],{},"所有从 GitHub 导入的数据都直接关联到您的 GitHub 应用安装。如果您卸载该 GitHub 应用，所有相关数据将被删除。",[229,380,381,382,386,387,391],{},"如果您删除 GitHub 仓库，关联的 Nuxt Studio 项目也将自动移除。但是，如果该项目订阅了团队计划，订阅不会自动取消。您需要通过 ",[240,383,385],{"href":384},"","Lemon Squeezy"," 手动结束订阅，或",[240,388,390],{"href":389},"team@nuxt.studio","联系我们"," 寻求帮助。",{"title":384,"searchDepth":393,"depth":393,"links":394},2,[395,396,401],{"id":235,"depth":393,"text":235},{"id":12,"depth":393,"text":12,"children":397},[398,400],{"id":276,"depth":399,"text":276},3,{"id":357,"depth":399,"text":357},{"id":375,"depth":393,"text":375},"Nuxt Studio 与 GitHub 原生同步。安装 Nuxt Studio GitHub 应用，并直接从 Studio 启用内容发布到 GitHub。","md",null,{},{"title":200},{"title":221,"description":402},"lSbOzVZpIMWfHroIFv3wds0QYAm7w1uXW2KY2fRDrgs",[410,412],{"title":196,"path":197,"stem":198,"description":411,"children":-1},"Studio 是用于编辑 Nuxt Content 网站的直观 CMS 界面。编辑你的 Markdown、YAML 和 JSON 文件，并将更改发布到 GitHub。",{"title":204,"path":205,"stem":206,"description":413,"children":-1},"发现并选择您喜欢的内容管理方式，视觉编辑器或代码编辑器。",1751727805660]